title: #212: Unpopular (@ThisDavidTaylor)
itunes:title: Unpopular with David Taylor
description: David Taylor came over to Benji's place in LA and we talked about him being unpopular. He's an unpopular person. Has been for years. And I've wanted to talk to him about it for years. And now I got the chance. So join us for a conversation about unpopularity and the Dirty Dancing soundtrack.
